name: Bridgetown: The Later Years (2013-2017)
description: Comics from the last five years of the Bridgetown perform, including: Allen Strickland Williams, Karen Kilgariff and Curtis Cook (2013), Steven Wilber (2014), Ismael Loutfi (2015), and John Novosad, Brad Silnutzer, Pat Brown, and Forrest Shaw (2017).
